78936a14f59826623fc01d","tid":2178074,"uid":142517,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T07:08:15.000Z","msg":"七生報國<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fwTQ4D2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfwTQ4D2.jpg&h=45e54d45&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"af1554de01c3d3d186e51ba3384b7c63a862bcd1","tid":2178074,"uid":266942,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T07:13:06.000Z","msg":"收信嘅人<br />\n<br />\n首先，用約100字自我簡介一下生平<br />\n<br />\n用200-400字講下你今生最開心嘅事<br />\n<br />\n用200-400字講下你今生最後悔嘅事<br />\n<br />\n用200-400字講下今生相遇嘅人<br />\n<br />\n用200-400字講下你自殺嘅原因<br />\n<br />\n用200-400字對在世嘅人留一d寄語<br />\n<br />\n最後，用約100字講下你對下一世嘅寄望<br />\n<br />\n寫低你個大名"},{"pid":"2e869a212c3e11b9b12df5451d2c6e9234593bf8","tid":2178074,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T07:36:16.000Z","msg":"多謝父母養育之恩<br />\n<br />\n自殺的原因<br />\n<br />\n交代你遺物同身後事點處理"},{"pid":"49f3b47f93e75036d04e713a4408ce5ad7008baf","tid":2178074,"uid":59134,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T07:40:13.000Z","msg":"寫俾你錫嘅同錫你嘅人睇<br />\n講下點解你要掉低佢哋<br />\n<br />\nPS 死唔可以解決問題 話唔定另一邊嘅生活更加辛苦"},{"pid":"d3936b77d166f4b895f16b2a3d963cf76a40fa07","tid":2178074,"uid":343986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd1699ceb04540b7e19fdedfd915e20f90fc377b","tid":2178074,"uid":305698,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T07:00:55.000Z","msg":"唔好放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T08:22:05.000Z","msg":"之前放棄過一次，今次唔會放棄自殺架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ddd7c891a30e497ba9b6cd59dd7e5ef0c1121ee","tid":2178074,"uid":343986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d56cc435c464922a809df2b0a40c16a16cf96c83","tid":2178074,"uid":300731,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T07:02:00.000Z","msg":"講下咩事？<br />\n<br />\n有人分擔下嘛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T08:23:53.000Z","msg":"都係錢，學業，前途之類"},{"pid":"e26cc0668edbee7aca42d67d4355ddf4a40d5c5c","tid":2178074,"uid":122513,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ab948fba2533ab38a2ce189fb0a4c7094f067fa2","tid":2178074,"uid":343986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T06:58:28.000Z","msg":"我係有預謀，有組織，有計劃想自殺，請問遺書寫咩好？謝謝。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T09:23:34.000Z","msg":"看來你心中的痛苦，已令你覺得生無可戀．．．人生之中往往有很多重要的決定，而自殺肯定是人一生中最矛盾、最痛苦，也是最重大的決定。我相信，自殺不是你想選擇的，更不是你唯一的選擇，只不過你所面對的困境和痛苦好像超越了你所能應付的，是嗎？<br />\n <br />\n無論你將會如何打算你的前路，我也希望你不要將困擾藏在心裡，好像氣球裡積存的壓力一樣。你不如停一停，<a href=\"http://到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%88%B0%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E7%9A%84%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99www.help4suicide.com.hk&d=7GjM3WQHKJNqnWTuO28XyHwvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=0c768ec8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。那裡有一些與自殺有關的人與事，你可以隨心看看（<a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk/myth_showlist.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk%2Fmyth_showlist.php&d=7GjM3WQHKJNqnWTuO28XyHwvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=374b61b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.help4suicide.com.hk/myth_showlist.php</a>）。 你更可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），即時與我們的義工在網上交談，或致電我們24小時電話熱線2389-2222，與我們的義工傾訴。<br />\n <br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n <br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"e257b49906508dc52d9c43e36f1005e29ae60e5a","tid":2178074,"uid":370165,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T13:23:34.000Z","msg":"求吓你唔好 你啲朋友會好傷心"},{"pid":"e347b0d69b228b89b12ed3a575dbfa04e72d3026","tid":2178074,"uid":345160,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T13:37:51.000Z","msg":"我前排都有段好想自殺<br />\n都出咗好多post<br />\n呢排心情雖然都係唔好<br />\n但總算叫比之前平靜好多<br />\n你比自己休息吓一段時間啦<br />\n真係會好好多"},{"pid":"1ee9