43e1c6c5cef1bb444546fb","tid":2178074,"uid":343986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53ab0fdf9d157e157c4c8629ce73ad2e5801cec2","tid":2178074,"uid":355782,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T09:06:06.000Z","msg":"點呀你<br />\n覆下呀～好擔心"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T10:43:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SEfPKXh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSEfPKXh.jpg&h=bd79c8dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最後的晚餐"},{"pid":"33d982981ee2f0aa506242b440eef75a76d922cc","tid":2178074,"uid":355782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T11:31:40.000Z","msg":"喂呀 唔好咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你以後仲有大把青春架大把機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有咩講出黎 幫你諗辦法解決呀"},{"pid":"e4a0df92e32b4bcd4bc81077634d5e59a52cf685","tid":2178074,"uid":350508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T12:13:31.000Z","msg":"咁多人支持你，唔好放棄自己啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然唔知你因咩事咁難受，但我作為曾經想死嘅過來人，真係好想好想同你講呢刻可能真係灰到極點，但其實只係光明嘅開始，依家諗番起昔日嘅我真係好傻。你喺到講俾我哋聽下你嘅心聲啊，咁多人可以同你一齊解決㗎！"},{"pid":"e51b8307cf7254f1772954c782f8c8a1cfb05f0e","tid":2178074,"uid":355782,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T13:15:54.000Z","msg":"How are u<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d326b904753c1fc0ec59a3506c0a1591b2a874f4","tid":2178074,"uid":199261,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T13:52:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ea04e5c699dcd2946dd1a7b94ca4d686967d00a7","tid":2178074,"uid":231486,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"75c0e35d8bedae7ad5441a6156590c454b7b5a34","tid":2178074,"uid":371984,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T07:08:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T15:54:52.000Z","msg":"你對對方認真嘅時候，對方視你嘅認真為笑柄。<br />\n呢啲朋友真係好差。"},{"pid":"c3f089d0716616c7a7d218e5ff915398ebccadf9","tid":2178074,"uid":363977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"baf2bfd063d951d139a99d946de2716a664c672e","tid":2178074,"uid":73026,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"e26cc0668edbee7aca42d67d4355ddf4a40d5c5c","tid":2178074,"uid":122513,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ab948fba2533ab38a2ce189fb0a4c7094f067fa2","tid":2178074,"uid":343986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T06:58:28.000Z","msg":"我係有預謀，有組織，有計劃想自殺，請問遺書寫咩好？謝謝。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T09:23:34.000Z","msg":"看來你心中的痛苦，已令你覺得生無可戀．．．人生之中往往有很多重要的決定，而自殺肯定是人一生中最矛盾、最痛苦，也是最重大的決定。我相信，自殺不是你想選擇的，更不是你唯一的選擇，只不過你所面對的困境和痛苦好像超越了你所能應付的，是嗎？<br />\n <br />\n無論你將會如何打算你的前路，我也希望你不要將困擾藏在心裡，好像氣球裡積存的壓力一樣。你不如停一停，<a href=\"http://到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%88%B0%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E7%9A%84%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99www.help4suicide.com.hk&d=7GjM3WQHKJNqnWTuO28XyHwvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=0c768ec8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。那裡有一些與自殺有關的人與事，你可以隨心看看（<a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk/myth_showlist.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk%2Fmyth_showlist.php&d=7GjM3WQHKJNqnWTuO28XyHwvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=374b61b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.help4suicide.com.hk/myth_showlist.php</a>）。 你更可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），即時與我們的義工在網上交談，或致電我們24小時電話熱線2389-2222，與我們的義工傾訴。<br />\n <br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n <br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T16:01:34.000Z","msg":"呢d copy and paste 既ads<br />\n我想自殺都唔會想禁入去傾啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T15:59:24.000Z","msg":"今次會員都唔打了"},{"pid":"933a3127d3d883bd96bb03168170cc2ddf01e437","tid":2178074,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cccfc1bd298316f5e2d96b57d35151d265c565be","tid":2178074,"uid":343986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf1c0da60586ba0714b07d90f4bdf4e0403bd5ca","tid":2178074,"uid":199261,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"d3936b77d166f4b895f16b2a3d963cf76a40fa07","tid":2178074,"uid":343986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T08:22:05.000Z","msg":"之前放棄過一次，今次唔會放棄自殺架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T16:34:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T01:16:44.000Z","msg":"未，預計今晚十點會跳，但未諗倒跳邊，不如一齊諗下？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. 公屋天台&gt;可能有鎖，但一定夠高<br />\n2. 大學&gt;要學生證先入倒，但可以non ju死入三大，完我心願<br />\n3. 商場入面&gt;太多人望住，難跳，但有冷氣<br />\n4. 高嘅行人天橋&gt;可能咁啱有車撞埋尼，咁個vector會變？冇車嘅就先落地再比車碌過，應該死硬<br />\n5. 多層停車場&gt;選擇少，會比人誤會我想偷車？但應該易跨過欄杆跳落去<br />\n6. 有露台嘅酒店&gt;唔知係咪一定book倒有露台嘅房，但喺酒店死都唔錯，好似去緊旅行錦<br />\n7. 跨海大橋&gt;點行上去？我唔識游水，應該好快浸死<br />\n<br />\n邊度跳好？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T16:00:54.000Z","msg":"點解要跳樓？<br />\n會斷手斷腳<br />\n唔靚仔"},{"pid":"3c7f86b42b9caad6e7cafa4057fef374bca52697","tid":2178074,"uid":231486,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ab948fba2533ab38a2ce189fb0a4c7094f067fa2","tid":2178074,"uid":343986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T06:58:28.000Z","msg":"我係有預謀，有組織，有計劃想自殺，請問遺書寫咩好？謝謝。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTim